===============
Uzewiki Changes
===============

Changelog
=========

0.1.0       2014-
            Feature:    Initial release


Roadmap
=======

Target
0.0.*       {% can_wiki [wiki_slug] %} ... {% else %} ... {% endif %} template tag
            Wiki create/edit view for admins
            "Manage wiki" section for admins
            * Edit wiki
            * Import and export
            Asset upload view
            Asset archiving
            ``convert_wiki`` to convert assets from dokuwiki
            ``convert_wiki`` to support more wikis (eg mediawiki)
            ``export_wiki`` to support a target wiki (eg dokuwiki, mediawiki)
            Test wikirest template tag, add wikimarkdown
            Support markdown
            Support ReST
            Integrate with timewarp
1.0.0       Stable release, make available on PyPI

The roadmap is subject to change; let me know if something is important to you.
